VIDEO3 What is Agentic AI? | Agentic AI using LangGraph | Video 2 | CampusX
Agentic AI: Autonomous AI that independently plans, decides, and acts to achieve goals.

Agentic AI components enable autonomous task execution.

Core Components

Brain: Reasoning/planning core (LLM) for decision-making.
​

Supervisor: Oversees multi-agent workflows, delegates tasks.
​

Orchestrator: Coordinates agent actions, manages flow.
​

Memory: Stores/retrieves context, experiences for continuity.
​

Tools: External APIs/functions for real-world actions
